{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after a while, you know, they brought in-- it was going already in-- into late 1940, '41.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They bought in Russian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were barracked in-- nearby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a while later, maybe a month and a half later, we were all locked in into the barracks, and nobody was allowed to go-- there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we heard shots, a lot of shots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the next morning, we saw the graves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the Russian soldiers were all shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were throwing them into graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, we had to-- to finish covering the graves, the pits, like.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were in pits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this camp became very bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they hung somebody, also, in the camp for committing some infraction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was not a very big crime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, being that we worked for a private company, the company where we built the barracks was also built by a private German company.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got very friendly with one of the head-- we call 'meister,' which is the foreman of the company.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got very friendly with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I knew they had another place in town, in Mlawa, by the railroad, where they used to do some work, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And some Jewish people used to work there, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they used to let them go home every day to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I pleaded with him, and I asked him-- I says to him that, you know, I have a mother and brothers and sisters that are in Mlawa, in ghetto, and I would like to go back to the other place there to work.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after a lot of begging, he transferred me to the other place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, I told him the whole story, that I'm a carpenter, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
